tutorial: Testing a Trading Idea - The Other Stages

definition.text: I'm sure that was a bit confusing! There are more than three nodes with messages, and messages are hard to relate to one another!

paragraphs.text: But don't worry! I'll help you figure this out!
First of all, remember that warnings are not errors!

We don't need to worry about warnings! Warnings are created every time the trading bot has to make adjustments to information that would otherwise not be obvious. It's kind of a verbose mode that the bot uses to leave a trace of its actions.
